snippet.title: Power Rangers Ninja Storm (Gameboy Advance) Playthrough Longplay Retro game
snippet.description: Power Rangers Ninja Storm is a side scrolling fighting game, based on the Power Rangers Ninja Storm TV show. The game uses passwords to track progress.[1]
